OL,7,FA sexual predator serving at least 36
OL,8,Fyears for the murder of primary school
OL,9,Fteacher Sabina Nessa stabbed a prison
OL,10,Fguard with a porcelain shard from a
OL,11,Fbroken toilet seat, a court has heard.
OL,13,FGarage worker Koci Selamaj, 37, was
OL,14,Falready serving a life sentence at
OL,15,FFrankland Prison near Durham when he
OL,16,Fstabbed the guard in May 2023.
OL,18,FNewcastle Crown Court heard how
OL,19,FSelamaj had smashed the toilet bowl in
OL,20,Fhis cell and used a shard from it to
OL,21,Fstab the guard.
