OL,7,FHe punched another officer two or
OL,8,Fthree times in the face as they came
OL,9,Fto the aid of their colleague, who had
OL,10,Fbeen stabbed in the knee and the
OL,11,Fforearm.
OL,13,FHe has since been moved to Broadmoor
OL,14,Fsecure hospital, which is where he
OL,15,Fwatched the proceedings in Court from
OL,16,Fvia videolink.
