OL,7,FThe 37-year-old garage worker was
OL,8,Fpreviously given a life sentence in
OL,9,FApril 2022 for murdering Ms Nessa, 28,
OL,10,Fas she walked though Cator Park in
OL,11,FKidbrooke, south east London, on her
OL,12,Fway to meet a friend.
OL,14,FHe carried out the sexually motivated
OL,15,Fmurder in September 2021 when he ran
OL,16,Fup behind Ms Nessa and hit her
OL,17,Frepeatedly over the with a metal
OL,18,Ftraffic triangle.
