OL,7,FThe court heard the stabbing at HMP
OL,8,FFrankland in May last year happened
OL,9,Fwith Selamaj in his cell when he was
OL,10,Fasked by a prison officer whether he
OL,11,Fwould be leaving for lunch.
OL,13,FThe defendant screamed and began
OL,14,Fsmashing up his toilet, before using
OL,15,Fpart of the seat as a weapon.
OL,17,FJudge Penny Moreland deemed the shard
OL,18,Ffrom the toilet seat to be sharp
OL,19,Fenough to be considered like a blade.
