OL,7,FIn a statement, the stabbed officer
OL,8,Fsaid he had never been assaulted in a
OL,9,Fdecade as a prison guard and added he
OL,10,Fhad loved his job.
OL,12,FHe described Selamaj's strength as
OL,13,F"unbelievable" and said he felt
OL,14,F"lucky" the attack was not more
OL,15,Fserious.
OL,17,FThe guard added: "Selamaj is in prison
OL,18,Ffor murder so I know what he is
OL,19,Fcapable of."
