OL,7,FDefending Selamaj, Aidan Harvey said
OL,8,Fthe life prisoner used to hear voices
OL,9,Fand thought "the electricity in the
OL,10,Fwall was talking to him."
OL,12,FMr Harvey added Selamaj's mental
OL,13,Fcondition has improved since beginning
OL,14,Ftreatment at Broadmoor.
OL,16,FSelmaj admitted wounding one guard
OL,17,Fwith intent to cause really serious
OL,18,Fharm at the maximum security jail, as
OL,19,Fwell as assaulting another occasioning
OL,20,Factual bodily harm.
