OL,7,FHe was sentenced to four-and-a-half
OL,8,Fyears in prison.
OL,10,FThe judge ruled he will only serve the
OL,11,Fsentence for attacking the prison
OL,12,Fofficers once he has completed the
OL,13,Fminimum term for murdering Ms Nessa.
OL,15,FHe will be at least 73 years old
OL,16,Fbefore he is eligible to apply for
OL,17,Fparole.
